      <p>Design functions to help solve the following problem. Use the answer guidelines in <xref text="title" ref="program-design_exercises_introduction"/>.</p>
      <p>The perceptual brightness of a color can be estimated with the formula:</p>
      <md>\text{brightness} = (0.2126 * R) + (0.7152 * G) + (0.0722 * B)</md>
